-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Mobile Stock Portfolio - This simple app displays a split view, with a portfolio on top, and a carousel on the lower half.  Touch swipe left/right in the lower half to see additional detail views and charts.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Authors: Yoshiroh Kamiyama (IBM CCLA), Christophe Jolif
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Demo description

	This demo displays a simple stock portfolio using dojox.mobile.SwapView.
	The screen is split into two panes using dojox.mobile.FixedSplitter.
	The lower pane can be scrolled both horizontally and vertically.
	
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Dependencies:

	Dojo Core
	Dojox Mobile

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Installation instructions

	Simply run the included demo.html
	
